OL,3,CAnger of families who paid thousands
OL,4,Cfor non-existent funeral plans
OL,6,FPeople who paid thousands of pounds to
OL,7,Fplan for funerals provided by a
OL,8,Fcompany at the centre of a police
OL,9,Finvestigation have spoken of their
OL,10,Fanger after discovering there is no
OL,11,Frecord of their policies.
OL,13,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors,
OL,14,Fin Hull, is being investigated after
OL,15,Fconcerns were raised about its "care
OL,16,Ffor the deceased" earlier this month.
OL,18,FThirty-five bodies were removed from a
OL,19,Ffuneral home on Hessle Road, along
OL,20,Fwith a quantity of ashes.
