OL,3,CAnger of families who paid thousands
OL,4,Cfor non-existent funeral plans
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of fraud and preventing a
OL,8,Flawful burial.
OL,10,FNow there are concerns that people who
OL,11,Fpaid to plan funerals for themselves
OL,12,For loved ones will lose out.
OL,14,FYvonne Colby and her late husband,
OL,15,FGeorge, thought pre-paying for their
OL,16,Ffunerals would ease the burden on
OL,17,Ftheir children.
