OL,3,CAnger of families who paid thousands
OL,4,Cfor non-existent funeral plans
OL,6,FHer daughter, Mekala, said: "I'm
OL,7,Freally angry about it. We aren't rich
OL,8,Fpeople, we're just every day working
OL,9,Fclass people who've worked hard for
OL,10,Fwhat we have.
OL,12,F"My mum and dad were making plans so
OL,13,Fthat me and my brothers don't have to
OL,14,Fworry about things, but now we do need
OL,15,Fto worry about things."
OL,17,FThe Colby family got in touch with
OL,18,Fpolice after news of the police
OL,19,Finvestigation was announced because of
OL,20,Fconcerns about the ashes they were
OL,21,Fgiven after George Colby was cremated.
