OL,3,CAnger of families who paid thousands
OL,4,Cfor non-existent funeral plans
OL,6,FThey say they have been assured they
OL,7,Fhave the right remains.
OL,9,FBut Mekala said the situation had
OL,10,Fcaused them a huge amount of stress.
OL,12,F"It's only been nine months since we
OL,13,Flost our dad, and he was our world,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"It all just comes to the surface
OL,17,Fagain - what you've already been
OL,18,Fthrough and now we're having to go
OL,19,Fthrough this as well. It's really
OL,20,Fhorrible."
