OL,3,CAnger of families who paid thousands
OL,4,Cfor non-existent funeral plans
OL,6,FJeff Richards and Maureen Rollinson
OL,7,Fhave also discovered their funeral
OL,8,Fplans do not exist.
OL,10,FThey each took out a plan out with
OL,11,FLegacy in 2015.JA handwritten receipt
OL,12,Fshows Mr Richards paid #4,200 by
OL,13,Fcheque.JHe said: "We decided that to
OL,14,Fsave our dependents having any
OL,15,Fproblems having to sort anything like
OL,16,Fthis out I had a bit of spare money
OL,17,Ffrom a retirement payment so I decided
OL,18,Fto invest it into a funeral plan, so
OL,19,Fwhen we did pass, our dependents
OL,20,Fwouldn't have any problems it would be
OL,21,Fstraighforward for them."
